# <type>(<scope>): <subject>
# |<----  Preferably 50 chars or less  ---->|
#
# <body>
# |<------- Try to keep each line 72 chars or less ------->|
#
# type:
#   feat     = 新功能
#   fix      = 修 bug
#   docs     = 文档/注释
#   chore    = 工程化（依赖/配置/样本数据）
#   refactor = 重构（不改功能）
#   test     = 测试
#
# scope (可选): 模块名或文件名前缀
#   e.g. huaye-walker, cron-scheduler, yueshe-business, zhuyueyunlu, apt
#
# 示例:
#   feat(huaye-walker): 房租催缴三档话术 + AI个性化生成
#   fix: 竞品价格采集携程页面解析失败
#   docs: 更新各模块安装说明
#